    <h1 class="name">Nahom Araya</h1>
    <h3 class="des">Hello, my name is Nahom Araya. I'm currently a student in Centennial College studying Software<br> 
        Engineering Technology. I'm currently in my 2nd year and is expected to graudate on 2025 december. This<br> 
